            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-tjb-rose-500 font-serif">04</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-tjb-charcoal mb-1">Postpartum care</h3>
              <p class="text-tjb-gray leading-relaxed">Breastfeeding support, placenta delivery, who you want in recovery, the first hours after birth, documented.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="py-5 border-t border-tjb-lavender-300/40 border-b">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[3rem_1fr] gap-4 md:gap-6 items-start">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-tjb-sage font-serif">05</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-tjb-charcoal mb-1">Newborn care</h3>
